Movie tells the incredible story of Takako Konishi, found frozen to death . 
 Body was found in Detroit Lakes, 50 miles from Fargo, in November 2001 . 
 Policeman she met thought she had been searching for suitcase of cash . 
 Steve Buscemi's crook buried one in the snow in 1996 Coen brothers film . 
 Rumour spread that Takako, 28, had tragically taken the tall tale to be true . 
 Kumiko, the Treasure Hunter tells story of this amazing version of events . 
 